OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and rain in the southeast
OL,6,Fsoon clearing, with sunny spells in
OL,7,Fthe west developing more widely. A few
OL,8,Fshowers are likely, these becoming
OL,9,Fmore frequent, heavier and blustery
OL,10,Ffrom mid-afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FScattered to frequent
OL,13,Fblustery showers feed in from the
OL,14,Fnorthwest through the evening and
OL,15,Fovernight, these showers heavy at
OL,16,Ftimes.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FIt will be quite cool and
OL,19,Fblustery with bright or sunny spells
OL,20,Fand scattered showers, these heavy at
OL,21,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
